description:
This is a 18 minute workout called 'Calisthenics for Complete Beginners (Tips, Exercise Form, Programming)' from the channel yvguo.
The workout falls under Strength/Calisthenics and Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Foundation Builder and The Progression Quest vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: This video is for complete beginners who are interested in starting their bodyweight training journey.

If you liked this video, and you are looking to boost your calisthenics/training journey by directly working with me for one-on-one coaching, hit me up on Instagram or Telegram:
